[Recruiting talents]

11
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:41,980
I need to tell you something.

12
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:44,140
The Su Family is hellbent
on recruiting talents.

13
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:45,740
They even asked the Right Chancellor Su
to join them for a while.

14
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:48,180
Everyone flocks toward them.

15
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:49,140
But look at us...

16
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:53,620
Su Rongqing strongly opposed
the imperial examination before.

17
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:55,020
But he changed his mind all of a sudden.

18
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:56,380
He's clearly trying
to steal talents from me.

19
00:01:56,660 --> 00:01:57,900
What did you say, Young Master?

20
00:01:58,260 --> 00:01:59,700
Before?

21
00:02:03,980 --> 00:02:05,500
That will cost a lot of money...

22
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,580
Hush now. Just go.

23
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:07,940
Go.

24
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:09,340
Okay.

25
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,860
Everyone. Everyone.

26
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:13,860
Well.

27
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:17,500
Her Highness and the Prince Consort said

28
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:20,140
that no matter whose article
was selected

29
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:22,460
would be awarded with one silver tael.

30
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:23,740
- One silver tael?
- One silver tael?

31
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,340
One silver tael.

32
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:25,500
This is better

33
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,580
than meeting the Right Chancellor.

34
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:27,260
Of course.

35
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:29,540
The Prince Consort
used to be a commoner,

36
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:32,220
so he knows what commoners
like us want better.

37
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,140
- That's right.
- That's right.

38
00:02:33,460 --> 00:02:35,100
I wrote this today.

39
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:36,140
Is this the place for signing up?

40
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:36,940
Yes.

41
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:40,260
Everyone.

42
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:41,140
Queue up.

43
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,460
My friend.

44
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,180
They are so passionate.

45
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,580
Money sure is more persuasive
than meeting the Right Chancellor.

46
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:49,340
Of course.

47
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:49,980
Oh my.

48
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,900
The expenditure here
will be paid with your wage.

49
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:53,780
I'm leaving.

50
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:56,140
Please no. My wage will never
be enough for this.

51
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,110
This is Prose Poem
of Discussing the Idea

52
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:59,660
that the same nature varies on nurture.

53
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:02,420
Whether people harbor
good or evil intentions

54
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:04,700
is determined
by their dispositions and habits.

55
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:07,100
Habits change as things change.

56
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,300
It can be especially shown
in their actions.

57
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,700
Disposition is an innate quality.

58
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:12,380
Calmness and contentment predominate.

59
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:13,300
This is the main point of this essay.

60
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:16,260
What a well-written passage.

61
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:18,340
Your Highness,
do you know that it is written

62
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:21,860
by a candidate who's going to attend
this year's imperial examination?

63
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:24,620
Your Highness,

64
00:03:24,940 --> 00:03:26,700
you'll be counting on them
in the future.

65
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,860
Consort Rou has arrived.

66
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:34,620
Your Highness, today's lesson
shall conclude hereafter.

67
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:36,820
Please finish your assignment.

68
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:38,500
Yes, sir.

69
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:40,460
Mr. Su.

70
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:41,860
Your Highness.

71
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:44,260
Cheng,

72
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,980
I wish to speak with Mr. Su in private.

73
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,060
You may leave now.

74
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:50,460
Sir, Mother,

75
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,700
I shall take my leave.

76
00:03:57,500 --> 00:03:59,020
Pei Wenxuan
is offering the candidates money now.

77
00:03:59,020 --> 00:04:00,420
It has had a big impact on us.

78
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:01,780
We should do something.

79
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:05,100
Calm down, Your Highness.

80
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,820
Just make sure your men

81
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:08,660
don't make any mistakes.

82
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,620
I will handle the rest.

83
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:11,660
You will be notified

84
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,620
immediately of any changes.

85
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,340
Thank you, Mr. Su.

86
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:18,260
I will do my best.

87
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:23,100
We are now waiting for great timing

88
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:26,380
before we can ask Prince Su

89
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,940
to recruit talents for us in person.

90
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:34,580
What brought you here, Mr. Su?

91
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:40,100
Mr. Shangguan, do you perhaps
have a candidate in mind

92
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,940
as the imperial examination's
chief examiner?

93
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:45,220
That's a decision
for the Ministry of Personnel.

94
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:47,580
It is a thankless job.

95
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:50,940
Ask Liu Hangchun to do it.

96
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:53,780
Liu Hangchun?

97
00:04:54,900 --> 00:04:56,700
He's not trustworthy.

98
00:04:56,780 --> 00:04:58,620
He often makes a lot of mistakes.

99
00:04:58,860 --> 00:05:00,980
If someone reports him,

100
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:02,940
it'll be...

101
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:06,580
Who do you suggest, Mr. Su?

102
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:12,460
My son, Rongqing,
is very interested in this matter.

103
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:15,380
I wonder if it's possible

104
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:16,260
to let him...

105
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:20,220
Mr. Su, His Majesty
promotes the imperial examination

106
00:05:20,300 --> 00:05:23,140
to contend
against the noble families like us.

107
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:26,300
The chief examiner cannot be one of us.

108
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:29,380
Therefore, we must find someone

109
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:30,900
who isn't from a noble family

110
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,260
but is willing to do our bidding.

111
00:05:43,380 --> 00:05:45,100
Your Highness, how is it?

112
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:48,300
You asked me to give you the signatures
of those handsome scholars.

113
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:49,420
But Pei Wenxuan isn't willing
to cooperate.

114
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,900
Forget about it now.

115
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:54,060
Just give me Liu Hangchun's case file.

116
00:05:54,460 --> 00:05:56,580
Your Highness,
you can't break your promise.

117
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:58,020
When did I promise you

118
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:59,180
that I'd bring the signatures back?

119
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,780
I did try for you.

120
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,100
Don't be insatiable.

121
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:06,060
But I told my friends
I would give them the signatures.

122
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:07,820
They were all so excited.

123
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,620
The case files you want are all there.

124
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:23,580
Any updates? Tell me.

125
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,260
[Liu Hangchun]
It's not just Liu Hangchun.

126
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:31,380
Su Rongqing

127
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:33,060
wants to do this job too.

128
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,460
Su Rongqing?

129
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:54,700
He used to look down on this.

130
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:58,820
Why the sudden change?

131
00:06:59,100 --> 00:06:59,820
Right.

132
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:01,900
The noble families looked down
on the examination candidates.

133
00:07:02,180 --> 00:07:04,540
But now, everyone wants them.

134
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:06,860
Based on what happened before,

135
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:09,740
this year's imperial examination

136
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:11,100
will be full of talented people.

137
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:14,100
Pei Wenxuan's disciples
will fill the imperial court

138
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,540
and he will become fully fledged.

139
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:20,660
So why is Su Rongqing meddling
in this suddenly?

140
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:21,900
Your Highness.

141
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:24,460
Your Highness.

142
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:27,220
It seems like

143
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:30,460
I have to secure Pei Wenxuan's
position as soon as possible.

144
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,300
When will you carry out your plan?

145
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:33,580
Now.

146
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,210
[Qingmei Restaurant]

147
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:38,620
Mr. Liu, I'm here.

148
00:07:38,660 --> 00:07:40,020
Come and catch me.

149
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:40,900
I'm over here.

150
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:41,660
I'm coming.

151
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:43,060
Mr. Liu.

152
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:45,300
I'm coming.

153
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:47,860
I'm over here, Mr. Liu.

154
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:50,740
Beautiful ladies, stop playing this

155
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:53,260
and come to me now.

156
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:56,620
If I catch you,

157
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:59,380
I'll punish you.

158
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,700
I...

159
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:07,700
I...

160
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,060
The Inspectorate Office
even cares about this?

161
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,500
Her Highness wants to see you.

162
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,620
Please come with me.

163
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:25,740
Greetings, Your Highness.

164
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:27,980
I did not know that you were here.
Please forgive me for the lack

165
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,260
of appropriate reception.

166
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:35,300
Mr. Liu, why are you so tense?

167
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:37,260
I'm here

168
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,940
to have tea with you.

169
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:40,820
No need to be so anxious. Please rise.

170
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,300
Thank you, Your Highness.

171
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:46,660
Take a seat.

172
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:59,260
You must be very busy lately, Mr. Liu.

173
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:00,540
It's all right.

174
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:02,420
I can tell.

175
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:08,420
I heard your spouse
recently gave birth to a son.

176
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:10,020
This is my gift to you.

177
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,260
Open it.

178
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,700
Please spare me, Your Highness.

179
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:26,100
Please don't give me a hard time.

180
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:27,140
Mr. Liu,

181
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:28,980
I'm not trying to give you a hard time.

182
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,580
I just need a favor from you.

183
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:34,180
I've heard you are in charge
of the mobilizations of officials below

184
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:35,780
the fifth rank
in the Ministry of Personnel.

185
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,900
I'd like to recommend someone,

186
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:39,740
Mr. Liu.

187
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:43,100
My consort is a talented man.

188
00:09:43,340 --> 00:09:44,380
If no one plays a dirty trick,

189
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:47,100
he can easily excel in the role
of a secretary of examinations.

190
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:48,420
So don't be scared.

191
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:50,900
I just want you to pay attention to him.

192
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:53,340
I know someone
might have talked to you already,

193
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:55,300
but I hope you

194
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:57,420
can make a sound judgment.

195
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,100
Your Highness,

196
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:04,940
I do not have a final say in this.

197
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:08,780
The Prince Consort must
rely on his talent

198
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:11,180
to earn that position.

199
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:14,020
I will handle this
with fairness and impartiality,

200
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,780
so please rest assured, Your Highness.

201
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,140
I am relieved to hear that

202
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:22,820
from you, Mr. Liu.

203
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,820
As you as you're satisfied,
Your Highness.

204
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:26,420
If there's nothing else,

205
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:29,620
I shall take my leave.

206
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:30,980
Take care, Mr. Liu.

207
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:37,980
Your Highness.

208
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,860
In a few days, the list
of staff mobilizations

209
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,860
within the Ministry of Personnel

210
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:42,540
will be out.

211
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:45,100
Once Liu Hangchun

212
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,300
adds The Prince Consort's name to it,

213
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:47,980
it'll be too late for Wang Houwen
to do anything

214
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,900
even if he gets hold of this.

215
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:52,620
Indeed.

216
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:55,820
Once the Ministry of Personnel
produces the list,

217
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:57,940
Ministry of Justice will release
its list of staff mobilizations soon.

218
00:10:58,540 --> 00:11:01,220
Pei Liming is doing the follow-up work
to Xie Lanqing's case.

219
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,740
So he should by right

220
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,460
be the Minister of Justice.

221
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:10,820
Young Master.

222
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,860
Any news from our informants?

223
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:13,580
Yes.

224
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,580
You asked them to keep an eye
on the Princess's Mansion.

225
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:17,060
They went to see Liu Hangchun.

226
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:24,180
It must be to get an in
with the Ministry of Personnel.

227
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:26,580
I need to know

228
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:28,700
whether it's Her Highness or Pei Wenxuan

229
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:30,620
went to that person.

230
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:31,780
It's Her Highness.

231
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:33,020
I see.

232
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:39,540
I was looking for an opportunity.

233
00:11:40,420 --> 00:11:41,420
Now,

234
00:11:42,540 --> 00:11:43,900
it presents itself.

235
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,660
Your Highness,

236
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:47,220
Second Young Master Su
sent a message saying

237
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,300
that he was setting up a trap.

238
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:51,140
Let me read it.

239
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,220
He asked you

240
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,700
to follow his plan.

241
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,020
He added that this operation

242
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:00,980
would test if you two can be allies.

243
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,300
Your Highness, just tell me the truth.

244
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,380
Are they handsome?

245
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:09,420
I didn't pay attention to them.

246
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:10,820
Why not? They are charming.

247
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:14,780
Your Highness, Miss Shangguan,

248
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:17,580
my young master asked me
to deliver this to you.

249
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,380
He did it!

250
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:27,340
Many handsome bachelors came

251
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:29,220
to Huajing for a forum.

252
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:32,020
I asked Su Ronghua

253
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:33,500
to get me their signatures.

254
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:37,540
Many noble ladies
are coveting their signatures.

255
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:40,260
It won't be a bad thing
to do them a favor.

256
00:12:47,020 --> 00:12:49,020
Su Ronghua is Huajing's
most handsome man.

257
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:51,340
Su Ronghua is charming.

258
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:53,620
Su Ronghua is not only handsome
but also talented.

259
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:57,300
You may hang this portrait
of mine in your chamber.

260
00:12:57,660 --> 00:12:59,180
It will brighten your day.

261
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:01,940
You want to do those ladies a favor?

262
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:06,100
Tell Su Ronghua

263
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,300
he's done for.

264
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:09,380
I shall relay this message verbatim.

265
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:23,180
Both of you want to see me today.

266
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:26,380
I am so honored.

267
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:28,220
May I know

268
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,340
what I can do for you.

269
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:31,540
Come on, Mr. Wang.

270
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:33,940
Thank you, Second Young Master Su.

271
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:36,460
Mr. Wang.

272
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,340
We came

273
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:41,140
to recommend someone
for the Ministry of Personnel.

274
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:45,740
Is that so?

275
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,660
You can just dispatch a messenger

